metadata.name: Karen Alternative - Yasashiku atsukau
metadata.description:
This is an alternate work from Karen's story.

Karen no yoru monogatari is the story of a young woman living in a city where night is always present.

Curious about the story?
https://www.karen-no-yoru-monogatari.com/the-story

This piece is the third project of the line works about her image. A tribute to the precious feature she has.

The drawing project is led by boppindrawing
Look at the Credit page:
https://www.karen-no-yoru-monogatari.com/team
